source: cli/tests/help.rs
expression: text
---
Print physical offset of first block and resume offset if file is suitable as
swapfile.

All conditions of swapfile extents are verified if they could pass kernel tests.
Use the value of resume offset for /sys/power/resume_offset, this depends on the
page size that is detected on this system.

Usage: map-swapfile [OPTIONS] <PATH>

Arguments:
  <PATH>
          Path to a file on the btrfs filesystem

Options:
  -r, --resume-offset
          Print only the value of resume_offset

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
